<!-- ========== P0 — CRITICAL / NOW ========== -->
<div class="tier tier-p0">
<div class="tier-hdr"><h2>🔴 P0 — Critical / Now</h2><span class="cnt">5 tickets</span></div>

<div class="ticket">
  <div class="ticket-id">FIN-001</div>
  <div class="ticket-body">
    <h3>Automate DAS invoicing</h3>
    <p>Auto-generate DAS invoices from booking data, eliminating the biggest manual time sink. Covers auto-detection of DAS items and invoice creation in Xero.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="ticket-meta">
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="tag">🧾 Invoicing</span></div>
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="badge badge-red">Jake + Dev</span><span class="effort effort-l">L</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ticket">
  <div class="ticket-id">FIN-002</div>
  <div class="ticket-body">
    <h3>Automate additions invoicing</h3>
    <p>Auto-identify additions vs original booking items and generate invoices accordingly. Removes manual classification and invoice creation for additions.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="ticket-meta">
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="tag">📦 Additions</span><span class="tag">🧾 Invoicing</span></div>
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="badge badge-red">Jake + Dev</span><span class="effort effort-l">L</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ticket">
  <div class="ticket-id">FIN-003</div>
  <div class="ticket-body">
    <h3>Design/spec the "winning" screen</h3>
    <p>Design the new winning flow UI — simplify the process, add validation checks, and use captured financial info to prevent downstream errors.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="ticket-meta">
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="tag">🏆 Winning</span></div>
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="badge badge-blue">Diego + Will</span><span class="effort effort-m">M</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ticket">
  <div class="ticket-id">FIN-004</div>
  <div class="ticket-body">
    <h3>Streamline & simplify post-event reconciliation</h3>
    <p>The whole post-event process takes too long due to cascading issues from earlier steps. Redesign the rec flow end-to-end to reduce manual effort.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="ticket-meta">
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="tag">🔍 Reconciliation</span></div>
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="badge badge-red">Jake + Dev</span><span class="effort effort-l">L</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ticket">
  <div class="ticket-id">FIN-005</div>
  <div class="ticket-body">
    <h3>Remove manual edits from Booking System for salespeople</h3>
    <p>Salespeople should not have to manually edit data in the Booking System. Auto-populate fields from the winning process and contract data.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="ticket-meta">
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="tag">🏆 Winning</span><span class="tag">⚙️ Operations</span></div>
    <div class="ticket-tags"><span class="badge badge-orange">Will + Dev</span><span class="effort effort-l">L</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>

