<!-- ========== OPEN QUESTIONS ========== -->
<div class="tier tier-q">
<div class="tier-hdr"><h2>❓ Open Questions — Decisions Needed Before Dev</h2><span class="cnt">17 questions</span></div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-001 · Commission % editable or locked?</h3>
  <p>Should commission % be editable after contract, or locked? Who can override — finance only, or also sales managers?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-002 · Mixed DAS/DAC on same booking</h3>
  <p>How do we handle bookings that contain both DAS and DAC line items? Split invoices or single invoice with mixed terms?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-003 · Commission guardrail ranges</h3>
  <p>What exact commission % ranges trigger warnings vs hard blocks? Should these vary by venue tier?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-004 · Guardrails: soft warnings vs hard blocks</h3>
  <p>For financial validation, which checks should be soft warnings (proceed with note) vs hard blocks (cannot continue)?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-005 · Commission rates source</h3>
  <p>Should commission rates always come from the contract, or allow manual override? What's the escalation path for overrides?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-006 · DAS check: block or advisory?</h3>
  <p>Should the DAS payment check be automatic (block payment until resolved) or advisory (warning only)?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-007 · Missing invoice flag timing</h3>
  <p>How many days after event should we flag a "missing invoice"? Should this be configurable per venue?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-008 · Rounding discrepancy tolerance</h3>
  <p>What tolerance threshold for rounding discrepancies before requiring manual review? What's the auto-journal limit?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-009 · Auto-journal approval</h3>
  <p>Who approves auto-journals for discrepancies? Finance manager, or auto-approve within threshold?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-010 · Juro API — auto-pull or manual?</h3>
  <p>Should Juro contract status pull automatically via API, or keep as manual sync with notification?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-011 · Dext integration scope</h3>
  <p>Integrate with Dext inbox directly for bill ingestion, or require manual upload? What's the reliability/cost trade-off?</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-012 · Xero bill status on creation</h3>
  <p>Should bills be created as Draft or Awaiting Approval in Xero? May depend on source confidence.</p>
</div>

<div class="q-ticket">
  <h3>Q-013 · Xero account code auto-suggestion</h3>
  <p>Auto-suggest Xero account codes based on booking type? What's the mapping logic and fallback?</p>
